.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Ignora saídas de build e pacotes do .NET (Backend)
**/[Bb]in/
**/[Oo]bj/
**/[Pp]ublish/
**/[Dd]ebug/
**/[Rr]elease/
*.csproj.user
*.dbmdl
*.efbundle
